messages.message: @nakul to raise visibility and start momentum to find a resource, I created and assigned https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/IBG-132 to you. Can you help identify an engineering resource to help with tooling to improve our UX for doc search? #fyi @georgia chestnuts rust-ing on an open fire and @marie and @Nithin and @Hari shared customer feedback that echoes the pain we all feel. I'm willing to partner for excellence! :thinking_face:
